Tolong jaga Seok Hoon
dan Seok Kyung hingga tiba masanya.

41
00:02:44,417 --> 00:02:45,817
Di mana dia?

42
00:02:56,874 --> 00:02:58,274
Setiausaha Cho,

43
00:02:58,299 --> 00:03:00,557
